  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Nanaya Clan<br /><strong>Description</strong>: You have mastered the Nanaya style of combat, and decided to modify it to better suit your tastes. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>increase your strength or dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>When casting a Nanaya clan Bukijutsu, that requires a melee taijutsu attack, while using a weapon with the thrown property, you can choose to throw your weapon and make a ranged taijutsu attack instead, and increase the range of the jutsu by 30ft. If the jutsu would allow you to move, you stop your movement before these additional 30ft.</li><li>Choose two Bukijutsu that you know, that require a melee or thrown weapon, and make a single taijutsu attack. The chosen jutsu become Nanaya Clan Hijutsu and gain the W (Simple Melee Weapon) keyword.</li><li>As part of casting a Nanaya Clan Hijutsu, you can move up to 10ft. This movement happens before the rest of the jutsu take effect.</li></ul>",
